---
const price = "Costo: $400 MXN";
const accountNumber = "Clabe Interbancaria: 002905905005317530 - Banco Banamex";
---
<section class="subscription-process">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="title">Proceso de Suscripción al Congreso</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Sigue estos pasos para inscribirte y asegurar tu participación.
    </p>

    <div class="price-box">
      <p class="price-text">💰 <strong>Costo:</strong> <span class="highlight">{price}</span></p>
      <p class="account-text">Depósito a: <strong>{accountNumber}</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps-container">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <h3>Depósito del Pago & Ingreso al Congreso</h3>
        <p>Realiza el pago correspondiente y obtén acceso inmediato al curso.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <h3>Llenar Formulario & Subir Comprobante</h3>
        <p>Completa el formulario de inscripción y adjunta la foto de tu comprobante de pago.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <h3>Acudir al Congreso</h3>
        <p>Presenta tu confirmación y disfruta del evento en vivo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<style>
  .subscription-process {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 50px 20px;
    background: #f8f8f8;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: auto;
  }
  .title {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: #222;
  }
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  /* 🔥 Sección de Pago */
  .payment-info {
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .payment-info .price {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #FFD700; /* Amarillo dorado */
    text-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.8);
  }
  .payment-info .account {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #444;
  }

  .steps-container {
    display: flex;
    gap: 25px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 10rem;
  }
  .step {
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 280px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .step:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 55px;
    height: 55px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e2de2, #4a00e0);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.4);
  }
  .step h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .step p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #666;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .subscription-process {
      height: auto;
      padding: 40px 15px;
    }
    .steps-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    .step {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 90%;
    }
  }
</style>
